Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.servertoclient.renderable.requests

Class GameNotFoundNotification

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.network.servertoclient.renderable.PrivateRenderable
it.polimi.ingsw.network.servertoclient.renderable.requests.Notification
it.polimi.ingsw.network.servertoclient.renderable.requests.GameNotFoundNotification
All Implemented Interfaces:
Renderable, java.io.Serializable
public class GameNotFoundNotification
extends Notification
This class represents a notification which is sent to the user when he tries to reconnect to a game and that exact game is already finished, so the user can't be reconnected to it.
